<div class="row">

  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="bs-component">
      <div class="well well-lg highlight_card">
        <h2><a href="<%= url_for new_lesson_path %>"> Create a Lesson</a></h2>
        <p>Share a lesson with the FIRST community. An example lesson is "Using a clamp". (Try to make them short and to the point. If it needs more time we recommend creating a course and adding the various lessons as part of one course.) </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="bs-component">
      <div class="well well-lg highlight_card">
        <h2><a href="<%= url_for new_course_path %>">Create a Course</a></h2>
        <p>Agregate lessons to create a course. This would enable users to have good understanding of a good concept. Example of a course is "FTC Robot Parts"</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="bs-component">
      <div class="well well-lg highlight_card">
        <h2><a href="<%= url_for new_track_path %>">Create a Track</a></h2>
        <p>Create a course track. Example of a track is 'Programming an FRC Robot'</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

